OL,5, The English National Opera is to move  
OL,6, its headquarters outside London and    
OL,7, have a drastic budget cut as part of a 
OL,8, major shake-up of English arts funding.
OL,10,FThe prestigious company will lose its  
OL,11,F#12.6m core annual grant from Arts     
OL,12,FCouncil England, instead getting #17m  
OL,13,Fover three years as part of a plan to  
OL,14,Frelocate, possibly to Manchester.      
OL,16,FIt's part of a wider overhaul to move  
OL,17,Fmillions of pounds from central London.
OL,19,FOthers to have lost their entire grants
OL,20,Finclude the Donmar Warehouse theatre.  
